dct_title_s: A map of Philadelphia and parts adjacent
dct_description_sm: This is state 2, lacking the table of distances and with more detail of the New Jersey shore and other engraving differences, of the map of the same title in Gentleman's Magazine, vol. 23 (1753), opp. p. 373. Shows rural buildings with occupants' surnames.
